    "name": "Cosmic Ultramarine",
    "steam_appid": 3296760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>化身飞升者，从高维度接入超次元，审视由你的数个前世构成的景观宇宙。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras/3a34e59ca9146470a45992fcb08d45e2.avif?t=1755675540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras_big/3a34e59ca9146470a45992fcb08d45e2.avif?t=1755675540 width=800 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >藉由一台移动终端展开漫游，从90s的网络空间到大西洋的马尾藻海；邂逅形形色色的生命——宇宙人、机械修道士，以及地球的最后一只恐龙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一切的尽头，宇宙、自我和生命的终极答案，将为你解开面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras/54ffd367e4e3ca5c63a8985d4ab44003.avif?t=1755675540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras_big/54ffd367e4e3ca5c63a8985d4ab44003.avif?t=1755675540 width=800 height=350 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一场没有压力的奇妙虚拟漫步。游戏无死亡及失败条件，所有的结局动画后，作为飞升者的玩家能够马上返回更早的时间线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras/aed637c8af2f00bf8fe47ec6db39ef75.avif?t=1755675540\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3296760/extras_big/aed637c8af2f00bf8fe47ec6db39ef75.avif?t=1755675540 width=800 height=242 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你抵达目标，百无聊赖时，你可以选择回到控制台房间，与你的好友Rain一同在网络世界中虚度时光，直至你想彻底回到现实。</p>",
